race.comment: BABA'S SWIFT (2) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 2.75 lengths (16.37) at Launceston. Key runner on her best form. UNLIKELY DANGER (3) was checked in the run and safely held when fifth (16.60) in a Grade 5 over 278m at Launceston. Better than last start and can bounce back. ROJO JOJO (6) found some support last start but struggled into seventh (26.99), beaten 11 lengths. Finished second the start before. Worth another chance. BREAKN' A SWEAT (1) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.
